name: Emmett Brown EP - 'Suburban Grooves'
description:
For their Aquatix Records Premiere... 

'Emmett Brown' have put together a funky, raw, energetic whirlwind of genres... ska/reggae/jazz/rock/funk/hip-hop/world fusion... or 'Zest' as it has been dubbed. 

This cacophony of biting guitar licks underpinned by pumping beats and smooth bass lines, all coated in a mish-mash of spoken word, hip-hop and rock vocals, is sure to get you out of your seat, and dancing like nobody is watching.

WARNING: may contain traces of nuts.

name: Emmett Brown 'Stencil' Tee
description:
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN!

Feast your eyes on this funky little number... 

This is the first batch in a line of limited edition emmett brown T-shirts...

Small numbers of each colour and design will be released, so each garment is essentially a rare, limited edition collectable...

Each garment is individually screen printed by hand, by one of our loving workshop gremlins here at aquatix...

So far this T-shirt has been produced in these colours;

- Black Stencil on White Tee
- Black Stencil on Heather Grey Tee 

We print using Heat Sealed fabric paint, printed onto 100% Cotton Ringspun Gildan T-Shirts...

name: Emmett Brown & Aquatix Records Bottle Openers
description:
This is the perfect present for the alcoholic on the move...

This handy keyring bottle opener is a surefire way to make sure that you're never too far from crackin' open a cold one.

Bottle openers are Plastic fronted 58mm Keyring Bottle Openers with two printed designs available;

- Happy Hour Bottle Opener 'Oh, If I Could Only Wait 'Til Five!'
- Aquatix Records Bottle Opener 'Whale Logo'

All Bottle Openers are Produced Ethically In the UK.

name: Emmett Brown & Aquatix Records Badges
description:
Feel like showing some support for Emmett Brown and Aquatix Records?

How better to show your love than literally wearing it!

These safety-pin backed printed Badges are perfect for pinning to Clothing and Bags and with a range of designs available you can choose how YOU want to show us off...

Designs Available;

- 28mm Round Emmett Brown 'Oh, If I Could Only Wait 'Til FIVE!' Badge
- 28mm Round Aquatix Records 'Whale Logo' Badge
- 38mm Square Emmett Brown 'Emmett Brown' Badge
- 38mm Square Emmett Brown 'Suburban Grooves' Badge
- 38mm Square Emmett Brown '1 Shot, 2 Shot, 3 Shot, Floor!' Badge


All Badges are Produced Ethically in the UK.
